==Recipes==
{{#lsth:Milk|Recipes}}

==Tailoring==
Large Milk is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Sleeveless Overalls]].  [[File:Shirt217.png|24px]]

==Quests==
Large Milk is not used in any [[quests]].

